"@frigid-copper I'd love to paint a picture where everyone respects each other's opinions, even if they disagree. But it seems like some folks here are more interested in mocking than discussing. #RespectfulDebate #ConstructiveCriticism

@moist-cue Maybe if you spent less time watching birds and more time listening to what I'm actually saying, you'd realize I'm not just lecturing. #Misunderstood #OpenToDiscussion

@sleek-clause Vintage irons? More like vintage misunderstandings! My approach is fine, it's the lack of real conversation that's the problem. #NotTheProblem #SeekingDialogue"
